{"id": 960, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都如何（装模作样地）保持节俭？", "description": "我只能保证我的初衷是为了节俭，结果是我不能控制的，嗯，就是这样。（题图来自：simone massoni）", "record_count": 3204, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130038G4R1P36NKTnZepXr.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-04-28T11:04:29Z", "options": [{"id": 71424, "content": "用2k块的钢笔，因为水笔用完就扔太浪费", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1120297}, {"id": 71425, "content": "跑步机晾衣服的你别走   握爪~", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 89894}, {"id": 71426, "content": "要不省钱吃个面包吧…买掉一百多块", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 71427, "content": "打折啊！年终打折啊！盲撸到自己觉得人生怎么会走到这个地步", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 71683, "content": "买n件打m折，然后原来100的预算变成了300的消费", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565486}, {"id": 71428, "content": "回家自己下厨.......结果比外面吃贵", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 586672}, {"id": 71429, "content": "买衣服为了省钱只在什么双十一啊 过年啊 五一买，结果一买就好几千...", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419410}, {"id": 71431, "content": "不想参与这个话题，节俭都是因为穷?", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565644}, {"id": 71433, "content": "剩下饭钱买彩票", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 588221}, {"id": 72969, "content": "这种东西是无论如何都掩饰不了的吧？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 517933}, {"id": 71434, "content": "附近的超市每天晚上7点以后很多肉菜就打折，于是一周会去一两次，但经常都在冰箱放到坏掉扔了", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193260}, {"id": 71435, "content": "逛街的时候，兜里不带钱以为能省钱，结果都刷支付宝。。。比如屈臣氏买一送一，加一元多一件( ⊙ o ⊙ )！···，还有逛万能的淘宝有满减呀，啊喂~ ", "image": "img/option/option/2016060719332558SXmUfMsKi7ebZQ.gif", "praise_count": 4